1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,990
[Episode 4]

2
00:00:05,730 --> 00:00:08,290
Never thought I'd have the chance
to meet Mr. Max up close.

3
00:00:08,290 --> 00:00:10,770
May I have the honor of toasting with you?

4
00:00:17,630 --> 00:00:18,570
Cheers.

5
00:00:47,570 --> 00:00:48,930
Need any help?

6
00:00:52,730 --> 00:00:55,410
Gentle wiping like this
won't remove it.

7
00:00:57,690 --> 00:00:59,170
You need to rub harder.

8
00:00:59,530 --> 00:01:03,570
Rubbing back and forth like this
will make it break.

9
00:01:04,810 --> 00:01:08,050
I mean, it will come off.

10
00:01:08,910 --> 00:01:12,510
After waiting for 18 years,
this day has finally come.

11
00:01:12,690 --> 00:01:16,310
And in a bathroom too.
How thrilling!

12
00:01:16,350 --> 00:01:17,680
Is this your first time?

13
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:19,090
Huh?

14
00:01:19,330 --> 00:01:22,110
We're screwed, Bin.
You can't let him know.

15
00:01:22,190 --> 00:01:23,750
So this is your first time.

16
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:27,390
You're so nervous.
Is this your first time at a club?

17
00:01:28,130 --> 00:01:30,930
Oh, yeah.

18
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:44,710
Wow, your hands
are shaking badly.

19
00:01:45,509 --> 00:01:47,640
Want to race to see who finishes first?

20
00:02:08,270 --> 00:02:09,949
Hey, Max.

21
00:02:09,990 --> 00:02:11,670
Why are you throwing up here?

22
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:18,750
[To Be Continued]
